    "data_size": 222,
    "nom_orig": "Maya",
    "texte_orig": "[U+1113]-kun,[SP]isn't[SP]that[SP]the[SP]door[SP]we[SP]came\nthrough[SP]a[SP]minute[SP]ago?[SP]Let's[SP]try[SP]going[SP]out\nthrough[SP]the[SP]other[SP]door.",
